  m_Text: "4. MONOBEHAVIOURS\n\nInside a MonoBehaviour subclass, you have access
    to some object instances as well. \n\ngameObject\n// A reference to the GameObject
    instance running the script\n\ntransform\n// A reference to the Transform of
    the GameObject instance running the script\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"
