    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "16. EXERCISE 5\n\nAutomated EvilCapsule Defense System\na) Find the AECDS
    object in the Hierarchy and its \"Defense\" script. Note its public \"enemies\"
    list attribute.\na) Find the HeatSeeker script on the EvilCapsule object. Edit
    it by overriding OnDestroy(), so that when the object is destroyed, it logs \"Ouch\"
    to the Unity console. Furthermore, edit the script so that when a new EvilCapsule
    is created, it is added to AECDS.Defense.enemies (use enemies.Add)\nc) Implement
    Defense so that whenever an enemy has distance < 2 to the Main Camera object,
    it is destroyed. \nHints: use Vector3.distance to measure distances between two
    transform.position."
