    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "11. GAMEOBJECT ACTIVATION\n\nIn the Inspector, you might have noticed
    that every object has a little checkbox in the top left. When the box is unchecked,
    the object name is greyed-out in the Hierarchy (try it!). In that case, the object
    will not be showed in the scene. \n\nAdditionally, if an object is de-activated
    when the game begins, its MonoBehaviours won't run Start() until its first activation.
    It is common to have a scene begin with several de-activated GameObjects, which
    won't activate until something happens."
