    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: '15. EXERCISE 4


    We''re going to show you some heat-seeking enemies!

    a)
    Find the de-activated EvilCapsule object in the Hierarchy

    b) Create an empty
    GameObject and attach a new script to it, called "Activator"

    c) Define a
    GameObject attribute which we may set from the Inspector, and feed the EvilCapsule
    object to it

    d) Now, implement Activator so that when the button A is pressed,
    5 copies of EvilCapsule are created into the scene. Then, each copy must be activated

    e)
    Give some space to the newly-created objects, increasing their transform.position.x
    by 2 each time'
