    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: '8. EXERCISE 2


    a) Create an empty GameObject.

    b) Create a script
    called "Repeater" attached to the empty GameObject

    c) In the Repeater class,
    define an attribute named "phrase" of type string, which may be edited from the
    Inspector

    d) From the inspector, set the value of the "phrase" attribute
    to "Hello, world!"

    e) Now, implement Repeater so that whenever the "Enter"
    button is pressed, we want the "phrase" attribute to be logged in the Unity console.'
--- !u!222 &1778256305
